    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S is a precision-engineered mid-engine platform powered by the 3.4L M97 flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus valve timing. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides an engaging, mechanical shift feel, paired with a chassis equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for adaptive damping. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers for consistent deceleration and thermal resistance. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity; recent service includes a cooling system overhaul and a documented bore scope to ensure cylinder wall integrity. While the exterior shows minor signs of use typical of a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain and suspension geometry remain tight and responsive, offering the tactile feedback and balance inherent to the 987 chassis.",
